WHAT ABOUT US

Welcome to EHA (Egypt Healthcare Authority Guide) App!

The Egyptian Healthcare Authority (EHA) was established under Act No. 2 of 2018 to oversee the Comprehensive Health Insurance System (UHIS).

As an independent body, EHA is committed to providing high-quality public healthcare services, consolidating and renovating healthcare facilities, and ensuring equal access for all Egyptians.

With a focus on professionalism, efficiency, and international standards, EHA aims to improve healthcare outcomes through innovative solutions, including the introduction of family medicine units and specialized treatment services.

The Authority also prioritizes enhancing healthcare quality and gaining the trust of the community by offering accessible, high-standard medical care across the country.
